   The article can be found in your system under the slug
BC-JOYCE-MAYNARD-SPEAKS-OUT-NYTSF. It has been sent to category
codes ``k,'' ``a'' and ``l.'' If purchased, the piece can be
published starting Sunday, June 20, or anytime thereafter.
