<DOCNO> NYT19990618.0182 </DOCNO>
<DOCTYPE> NEWS STORY </DOCTYPE>
<DATE_TIME> 1999-06-18 13:49 </DATE_TIME>
<HEADER>
A0790 &Cx1f; tdt-z
u e &Cx13;  &Cx11;  BC-MUSIC-BIZKIT-BOS &LR;      06-18 1151
