 Friday, June 18, 1999    
 Editors      The Hearst News Service has filed or will file the
following for Saturday and Sunday. If you have questions, please
call Susie McBee or Tim Spence at 202-298-6920. For questions about
Houston Chronicle sports stories, please call 713-220-7896. (The
``HNS'' tag appears in all sluglines.)   
