(gm) 
<TEXT>
<P>
   We commend to your attention a lengthy profile of George W. Bush
from our partner  &UR; Cox News Service &LR;  for release Sunday, June 20.
</P>
<P>
   Written from Austin, Texas, by Patick Beach, the 6750-word
profile is in three takes, slugged BUSH-PROFILE-COX-TAKE1,
BUSH-PROFILE-COX-TAKE2 and BUSH-PROFILE-COX-TAKE3. In addition,
there is a 325-word sidebar, BUSH-TIMELINE-COX, listing significant
events in his life.
</P>
<P>
   And there is a shorter version, BUSH-PROFILE-SHORT-COX, at 2875
words. This version is also available for sale as a full-page
layout at www.nytsyn.com/pageexpress.
</P>
<P>
   The profile and sidebar moved with a ``p'' category code and
will be repeated following this advisory.
</P>
<P>
   Three photos (NYT2, NYT3 and NYT4) have been sent on Friday to
NYT photo clients. Non-subscribers can make individual purchase by
calling (888) 603-1036 or (888) 346-9867.
</P>
<P>
   &UR; QUESTIONS OR RERUNS: (888) 346-9867 or (212) 556-1927: &LR;
</P>
<P>
   The day supervisor is Gary McCardell.
</P>
<P>
   The evening supervisor is Henry Warnken.
</P>
<P>
   The late-night supervisor is Ray Krueger.
