   DISNEY-TARZAN &QL;
</P>
<P>
   DALLAS _ Disney has done it again, with an epic retelling of
Edgar Rice Burroughs' immortal ape-man, ``Tarzan.'' As with many of
its best animated offerings, the studio has invented new technology
to broaden the range of animation. With their latest film, it's
Deep Canvas, a computer-driven technique that gives their agile,
more simian Tarzan the appearance of swinging through a
three-dimensional forest. By TODD CAMP. Story will move in ``e''
entertainment category. (Accompanied by TARZAN-OTHER ANIMATION.) &QL; 
 &QL; 
 &QL;
</P>
<P>
   FILM-BROTHERS QUINN &QL;
</P>
<P>
   DALLAS _ For Aidan Quinn and Paul Quinn, the new movie ``This Is
My Father'' gives new meaning to ``family film.'' Aidan stars in
the movie, which was written and directed by Paul, with their
brother Declan acting as cinematographer. The Quinns discuss their
movie, their family and their Irish roots. By ROBERT PHILPOT. Story
will move in ``e'' entertainment category. &QL; 
 &QL; 
 &QL;
