<P>
   UNDATED _ My fourth Father's Day was rapidly approaching, and I
found myself conflicted. What, pray tell, did I want? My wife's
favorite Mother's Day gift is an afternoon at the Galleria _
without the kids. She thinks Mother's Day is Independence Day, with
a credit card. With two precocious children, ages 4 and 20 months,
I was beginning to understand the appeal of peace and quiet _
whatever that might be _ but I just wasn't sure. By BUZZ MCCLAIN.
Story will move in ``l'' lifestyle category. &QL; 
