<HEADLINE>
(EDS: DISNEY-TARZAN) 
COMING CARTOON ATTRACTIONS
</HEADLINE>
 (For use by NYTimes News Service clients) 
c.1999 Fort Worth Star-Telegram 
<TEXT>
<P>
   It hasn't been much of a year for animation thus far: Warner
