   &QL; 
MIGS _  &UR;  &LR; Two United Airlines pilots have spent thousands of hours
restoring two rare MiG17s. With a boost from a Russian vodka
company, the pilots are flying the planes in air shows. By Rebecca
Smith
</P>
</TEXT>
</BODY>
<TRAILER>
